{"tid":2159563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[下集] 椰青蒸蟹 + 桃撻","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:55:16.000Z","uid":340796,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"33496506c037dcd51564345658e44ca2887464b6","tid":2159563,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"早兩星期睇cable 教整椰青蒸蟹<br />\nHKTV $35/2個椰青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起肉, 留底椰水, 加蛋白<br />\n放隻肉蟹上去蒸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTU7gHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTU7gHJ.jpg&h=77ffc9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲整咗兩日嘅水蜜桃撻<br />\n買咗2個日本桃<br />\n焗咗個底先, 牛油皮+杏仁filling<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FprhDWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFprhDWY.jpg&h=bf5c7f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舗埋custard +氧化咗嘅桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唧埋cream 就搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxCXDXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxCXDXt.jpg&h=78afdd08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f79K3tc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff79K3tc.jpg&h=57ad05b4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n樣衰啲但好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點樣先可以keep 到桃唔氧化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58da1800eb7b49e401a5093c2758ffd3ea092c0e","tid":2159563,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"個撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feba996c1e15b5e21e46e6ee0edc0a4e2490b49a","tid":2159563,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pi